cat << EOF
TeX Live is an easy way to get up and running with the TeX document production system. It provides a
comprehensive TeX system with binaries for most flavors of Unix, including GNU/Linux, and also Windows.
It includes all the major TeX-related programs, macro packages, and fonts that are free software,
including support for many languages around the world.

WARNING: the source tarball is more than 1.1Gb so make sure you have space!
